Chief Whip of the Senate and two-term Governor of Abia State, Senator Orji Uzor Kalu is currently in a closed-door meeting with the Governor of Abia State, Dr Okezie Ikpeazu Ikpeazu received Senator Kalu at his Umuobiakwa country home at Obinngwa LGA, Abia state Okezie Ikpeazu alongside his aides and personal staff who were already waiting for Kalu’s coming received the Senate Chief Whip who arrived at the Governor’s mansion at exactly 1:32 pm. Shortly after the pleasantries, Governor Ikpeazu then proceeded into an inner room with Orji Kalu for a private meeting. Details soon…